name: POUFF_ Face with Neon Pink polka dots + Black & White motif side
description:
Hand made in Australia, using 100% rescued fabric.

Each pouff is unique and made from a medium weight, durable cotton.

Can be stuffed with fabric off-cuts to create a firm and sturdy pouff, or filled with polystyrene beans for a lighter seat.
Fitted with a hidden zip at the side for easy filling and closing.

Measures
470mm diametre
220mm height

Please Note
All pouffs listed on my online store are sold FLAT (unstuffed)
